  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "两处访问",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25169102_8_26205-26260",
          "range": "26205-26260",
          "rangeStart": 26205,
          "rangeEnd": 26260,
          "markText": "，而那是正当一个女人到处看不见怜悯和安慰的目光的时候。在这种情形之下，一个男人对女子说温柔的话，一定是别有用心",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1616064914,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2021-03-18 18:55:14",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169102&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=26205&rangeEnd=26260",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2da32cf071800cce2daeab3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=26205&rangeEnd=26260"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25169102_8_10478-10583",
          "range": "10478-10583",
          "rangeStart": 10478,
          "rangeEnd": 10583,
          "markText": "欧也纳不知道在巴黎不论拜访什么人，必须先到主人的亲友那里，把丈夫的，妻子的，或儿女的历史打听明白，免得闹出笑话来，要像波兰俗语所说的，把五头牛套上你的车！",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1616064910,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2021-03-18 18:55:10",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169102&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10478&rangeEnd=10583",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2da32cf071800cce2daeab3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10478&rangeEnd=10583"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25169102_8_17036-17074",
          "range": "17036-17074",
          "rangeStart": 17036,
          "rangeEnd": 17074,
          "markText": "可不是！这家伙有两个女儿，他都喜欢得要命，可是两个女儿差不多已经不认他了。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1616064909,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2021-03-18 18:55:09",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169102&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17036&rangeEnd=17074",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2da32cf071800cce2daeab3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=17036&rangeEnd=17074"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25169102_8_21001-21058",
          "range": "21001-21058",
          "rangeStart": 21001,
          "rangeEnd": 21058,
          "markText": "有些女人，只喜欢别的女子挑中的男人，好像那班中产阶级的妇女，以为戴上我们的帽子就有了我们的风度。所以那时你就能走红",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1616064909,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2021-03-18 18:55:09",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169102&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=21001&rangeEnd=21058",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2da32cf071800cce2daeab3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=21001&rangeEnd=21058"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25169102_8_2022-2044",
          "range": "2022-2044",
          "rangeStart": 2022,
          "rangeEnd": 2044,
          "markText": "这时高老头从小扶梯的出口，靠近大门那边出现了",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1616064908,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2021-03-18 18:55:08",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169102&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2022&rangeEnd=2044",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2da32cf071800cce2daeab3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2022&rangeEnd=2044"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "初见世面",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25169102_9_13613-13663",
          "range": "13613-13663",
          "rangeStart": 13613,
          "rangeEnd": 13663,
          "markText": "人生就是这么回事。跟厨房一样腥臭。要捞油水不能怕弄脏手，只消事后洗干净；今日所谓道德，不过是这一点。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1616064913,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2021-03-18 18:55:13",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169102&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13613&rangeEnd=13663",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2da32cf071800cce2daeab3?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=13613&rangeEnd=13663"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25169102_9_21110-21204",
          "range": "21110-21204",
          "rangeStart": 21110,
          "rangeEnd": 21204,
          "markText": "亲爱的先生，你怎么能以为说出了我的名字，特·雷斯多太太便生你的气呢？两个女儿都很孝顺，我是个幸福的父亲。只是两个女婿对我不好。我不愿意为了跟女婿不和，教两个好孩子伤心，我宁可暗地里看她们。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1616064912,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2021-03-18 18:55:12",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25169102&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=21110&rangeEnd=21204",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2da32cf071800cce2daeab3?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=21110&rangeEnd=21204"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "25169102_9_9867-9894",
          "range": "9867-9894",
          "rangeStart": 9867,
          "rangeEnd": 9894,
          "markText": "两个人中间有一个多余的时候，只有傻瓜才会听凭偶然去决定",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1616064912,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2021-03-18 18:55:12",
